data.description: Don't miss out on the opportunity of country living in Apex, NC! This single family home, on almost 4 acres, is like new with renovations and updates! Recently renovated kitchen, dining room, and mud room (laundry and 1/2bath)! New paint throughout the interior and exterior of the home. Featuring the owner's suite on the first floor with French doors leading to the deck. Enjoy your evenings sitting on the back porch with only the sound of nature. Following that enjoy the upstairs entertainment area complete with pool table, perfect for get togethers! CAT5 is wired throughout the home for all your internet, gaming or work from home needs. The home also offers tons of Smart Home accommodations. RV/boat outbuilding with water and power located in the backyard with a second access entrance. Backyard is partially fenced for little ones or furry friends.
